high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the frying pan to the right of the toaster.
Turn around and walk to the sink on your left and face it.
Wash the frying pan in the sink then take it back out and turn off the water.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left.
Put the pan to the right of the head of lettuce with the handle pointing to the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean frying pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter, then turn left and face the toaster.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Place the pan on the counter to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pan on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left to move to the counter and then turn your body left to face the counter area with the toaster.
Pick up the pan to the right of the toaster.
Turn around to move in front of the sink.
Place the pan in the sink, turn on the water, and then remove it once cleaned.
Carry the pan to stand in front of the dishwasher, which is the right of the sink.
Place the pan on the back of the counter by the wall, and right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed pan on the counter.
